      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a fisherman.\n1. The applicant must have a valid Family Identity Card (Parivar Pehchan Patra).\n1. The applicant should be engaged in fishery-related activities.\n1. The applicant must ensure proper operation and maintenance of the vending center.\n1. The applicant will receive assistance for only one live fish vending center.\n1. The government will not be responsible for any operational loss or damage.\n\n",
